# Task / plan validation (LOCKED — always-on · all agents)

**SSOT:** `data/sourcea-next-task-trigger-v1.json` v2.0.0  
**Machine:** `scripts/next_task_trigger_v1.py`  
**Validator:** `bash scripts/validate-next-task-trigger-v1.sh`  
**Always flag:** `~/.sina/task-plan-validation-always-v1.flag`

## One law

> **Every agent discussing ANY task or plan must run the tiny validation pipeline — not only on NEXT TASK trigger. Validate before proceed.**

Applies whenever founder or agent talks about: backlog rows · work orders · upgrade plans · Cloud Forge Run · B#### · sa-mkt-#### · CLOUD-SEC-### · execute/proceed · usefulness · real-world output.

## Trigger phrases (also activate explicit NEXT TASK mode)

**next task** · **NEXT TASK** · **what is the next task** · **finish the next**

## Mandatory sequence

**Every session (baseline):**

```bash
python3 scripts/next_task_trigger_v1.py --refresh --json
```

**When founder message or task id is known:**

```bash
python3 scripts/next_task_trigger_v1.py --activate --text "<founder message>" --json
python3 scripts/next_task_trigger_v1.py --refresh --task-id B0006 --json
python3 scripts/next_task_trigger_v1.py --refresh --plan-id sa-mkt-0003 --json
```

Read receipt `pipeline` block. Reply MUST include:

| Section | Agent answers |
|---------|----------------|
| **What is this task?** | Resolved id(s) · title · cloud_action · resolution source |
| **Benefit and priority** | P0–P4 stack · north-star fit · because/so |
| **Real-world output** | Type: `file_generation` · `marketing_system` · `ai_agent_product` · `data_pipeline` · `internal_meta` |
| **Usefulness verdict** | `useful` · `noise` · `blocked` · `needs_founder_answer` |
| **Proceed?** | `yes` · `no` · `wait` · `ask_founder` |

## Required founder question (state once)

> What is the real-world output supposed to be?

## Forbidden (always)

- Discussing or executing a task/plan without pipeline sections
- Marking `cloud_proof` when verdict is `noise`
- Queue drain without usefulness verdict
- Treating internal_meta receipt as product progress

## Applies to

SourceA Brain · SourceA Worker · any Cursor agent in `~/Desktop/Noetfield-Systems/SourceA`

